tags.name: 110kV Kilbarry Electrical Substation
tags.note:
New GIS building under construction, which will take over the Coolroe, Carrigadrohid, Mallow and Knockraha 2 connections. 
This station was built in the early 1950s, replacing a smaller one dating back to the Shannon scheme.

tags.name: Carrigadrohid 110kV Substation
